discourse_list.title: Glass Entertainment Group's Q&A -- MakerDAO Content Creation (Every Monday -- 5 PM ET)

content.content: Please join Glass Entertainment’s Q&A weekly call, every Monday at 5 PM ET. We look forward to having the community join to ask us questions about our current informal poll, our company and our vision for content creation for MakerDAO. Below is the link to join:    meet.google.com   Google Meet (formerly Hangouts Meet) - Free Video Meetings Use Google Meet (formerly Hangouts Meet) video conferencing solutions from your browser or mobile app. Get started with a secure, HD video today.
